 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Speed-boost:

    This Pokémon's Speed rises 
  one stage after each turn.

  Compound-eyes:

    This Pokémon's moves have 1.3× 
  their accuracy.

  This ability has no effect 
  on the one-hit KO moves (fissure, 
  guillotine, horn drill, and sheer 
  cold).

  Overworld: If the first Pokémon 
  in the party has this ability, 
  the chance of a wild Pokémon 
  holding a particular item is 
  raised from 50%, 5%, or 1% to 
  60%, 20%, or 5%, respectively.

  Frisk:

    When this Pokémon enters battle, 
  it reveals an opposing Pokémon's 
  held item to all participating 
  trainers.

  In a double battle, if one 
  opponent has an item, this Pokémon 
  will Frisk that Pokémon; if both 
  have an item, it will Frisk one 
  at random.


